	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="min-height:55vh;background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/best-catering-vancouver.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Best Indian Dishes<br/>for <em>Corporate Lunches</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">The crowd-pleasers that always work, and why.</p>
		</div>
